{"tid":1075780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜變「南韓瑜」 澳門中聯辦新聞稿瘀爆出錯","createTime":"2019-03-24T11:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T13:09:30.000Z","uid":103981,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8b9b5b18e4b09a4aaa07ad24d1782d3aa99f4c6e","tid":1075780,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:27:47.000Z","msg":"國民黨的台灣高雄市長韓國瑜訪問香港和澳門中聯辦，惟澳門中聯辦昨晚（23日）在網站發佈的繁體版新聞稿，標題和內文均將韓國瑜打錯為「南韓瑜」，至今日下午2時半仍未修正，簡體版則未有出錯。在《蘋果》報道上載後，記者下午4時再登入網站查看，發現「南韓瑜」終被修正。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【韓流「襲」深圳】行程好神秘！ 記者團酒店booking「被取消」<br />\n<br />\n澳門中聯辦昨晚10時許，在網站發表題為《傅自應會見高雄市市長南韓瑜》的新聞稿，內文指「中央政府駐澳門聯絡辦公室主任傅自應在新竹苑，會見台灣高雄市市長南韓瑜率領的高雄市參訪團&hellip;&hellip;對南韓瑜一行來澳門進行城市交流表示歡迎&hellip;&hellip;南韓瑜感謝傅自應主任的熱情接待」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190324/large/1553414379_3e15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190324%2Flarge%2F1553414379_3e15.jpg&h=df613ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190324/59405844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190324%2F59405844&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8rtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=83db09b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190324%2F59405844&h=128da315\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190324/59405844</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}